data.description: Let's start with this gorgeous kitchen with upgraded countertops, 5 burner gas stove with convection oven, with upgraded LVP.  Spacious living room with upgraded carpet.  Virtually costs nothing for electricity because it has solar!  New water softner with reverse osmosis.  Security doors on the front entrance door and the garage man door.  Back and front yards fully landscaped with automated drip system, plenty of space for those bbq's.  This is a must see home. Too many upgrades to list.  Come and check this beautiful well cared for home in a great subdivision just 25 minutes from USA Parkway.  The community has a park for all to use. Lease on solar is $96.00, current electric bill is $17.43. Upgraded pad and carpet, upgraded LVP, finished back yard.  Seller is leaving flag pole with a new flag for the new owner.  This home is spotless and ready to move in.
